data.title: Norway's Mol, Sorum win men's beach volleyball gold
data.meta_description: Norway's Anders Mol and Christian Sorum took down Viacheslav Krasilnikov and Oleg Stoyanovskiy of the Russian Olympic Committee to win beach volleyball gold at the Tokyo Olympics.
